10
00:00:48,554 --> 00:00:53,664
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Shower me with a strong love that hurts</i></b></font>

11
00:00:53,664 --> 00:00:55,394
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Blazin' beat</i></b></font>

12
00:00:55,394 --> 00:01:00,104
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Embrace the echo in the crying wind</i></b></font>

13
00:01:00,104 --> 00:01:03,504
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Naked mind and desire</i></b></font>

14
00:01:03,504 --> 00:01:06,844
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Wanting is not a crime</i></b></font>

15
00:01:06,844 --> 00:01:13,854
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Leave your worries behind and trust me</i></b></font>

16
00:01:13,854 --> 00:01:18,084
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Blazin' beat! Yo! Let's go wild</i>
<i>and throw away our morals</i></b></font>

17
00:01:18,084 --> 00:01:19,854
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Break loose impulsively</i></b></font>

18
00:01:19,854 --> 00:01:21,454
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>It's the weekend, everybody gather around!</i></b></font>

19
00:01:21,454 --> 00:01:24,794
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>M.O.V.E., move, break ahead</i>
<i>of the pack and go crazy</i></b></font>

20
00:01:24,794 --> 00:01:28,254
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Let's look for explosive thrills, it's the time!</i></b></font>

21
00:01:45,044 --> 00:01:47,714
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>They're coming into the first corner.</b></font>

22
00:01:47,714 --> 00:01:50,554
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>The Evo IV is following?!</b></font>

23
00:02:07,174 --> 00:02:09,774
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>No matter how well you turn corners...</i></b></font>

24
00:02:09,774 --> 00:02:12,574
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>...you're just an Eight-Six.</i></b></font>

25
00:02:25,054 --> 00:02:28,894
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Anyone driving a junker like
an Eight-Six is beneath me!</b></font>

26
00:02:28,894 --> 00:02:32,194
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I wouldn't race them even if they asked.</b></font>

27
00:02:33,194 --> 00:02:35,064
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>But the car...</b></font>

28
00:02:35,064 --> 00:02:38,304
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I'd have to say the Eight-Six
is no longer good enough.</b></font>

29
00:02:38,304 --> 00:02:41,374
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>We will never lose.</b></font>

30
00:02:41,374 --> 00:02:43,934
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>The king of mountain passes is the Lan-Evo!</b></font>

31
00:02:47,074 --> 00:02:51,304
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>No one knows who will win</i>
<i>until we actually race!</i></b></font>

32
00:03:01,624 --> 00:03:05,324
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="66"><b>{\an5}"Act 3: Premonition of Defeat"</b></font>

33
00:03:06,424 --> 00:03:09,664
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>With the speed of the Evo IV,
Seiji should take the lead</b></font>

34
00:03:09,664 --> 00:03:12,364
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>before the first corner, despite his late start.</b></font>

35
00:03:12,364 --> 00:03:16,374
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>That wasn't even Seiji's full start, though.</b></font>

36
00:03:16,374 --> 00:03:18,504
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>He stayed behind on purpose?</b></font>

37
00:03:18,504 --> 00:03:21,014
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Is he on "Simulation 2"?</b></font>

38
00:03:21,014 --> 00:03:24,014
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Offensive-minded Seiji is being very careful.</b></font>

39
00:03:24,014 --> 00:03:27,014
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>No need for that against an Eight-Six.</b></font>

40
00:03:27,014 --> 00:03:30,184
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>"Simulation 1" should be enough to beat him.</b></font>

41
00:03:30,184 --> 00:03:32,354
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Not necessarily.</i></b></font>

42
00:03:32,354 --> 00:03:35,854
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Seiji is a top-notch racer, but he's not clever.</i></b></font>

43
00:03:35,854 --> 00:03:41,194
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>So far, all his races were easy,</i>
<i>so he's getting careless.</i></b></font>

44
00:03:41,194 --> 00:03:44,604
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>"Simulation 3" is to tighten his loose mind.</i></b></font>

45
00:03:44,604 --> 00:03:46,464
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Don't fail me, Seiji.</i></b></font>

46
00:03:46,464 --> 00:03:48,934
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Stumbling here before facing Ryosuke...</i></b></font>

47
00:03:48,934 --> 00:03:50,704
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>...is unacceptable.</i></b></font>

48
00:04:19,934 --> 00:04:22,734
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Maybe it's too much to ask.</b></font>

49
00:04:22,734 --> 00:04:26,674
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Basically, the Evo IV is a WRC rally car.</b></font>

50
00:04:26,674 --> 00:04:30,344
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It's light, and is equipped with turbo and 4WD.</b></font>

51
00:04:30,344 --> 00:04:34,184
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>On top of that, the driver
has first-class technique.</b></font>

52
00:04:34,184 --> 00:04:35,954
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Takumi can't win.</b></font>

53
00:04:35,954 --> 00:04:39,854
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Come on, Iketani and Kenji!</b></font>

54
00:04:39,854 --> 00:04:44,964
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Why are you always so
pessimistic about things?</b></font>

55
00:04:44,964 --> 00:04:46,624
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>But, Itsuki...</b></font>

56
00:04:46,624 --> 00:04:49,734
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It's Takumi who is racing!</b></font>

57
00:04:49,734 --> 00:04:51,304
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Unlike others,</b></font>

58
00:04:51,304 --> 00:04:55,104
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Takumi always makes
something happen when he races.</b></font>

59
00:05:19,594 --> 00:05:22,764
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Damn, I don't like this.</i></b></font>

60
00:05:22,764 --> 00:05:27,064
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>This is irritating. Damn it!</i></b></font>

61
00:05:58,134 --> 00:06:00,534
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Hey, Papa?</b></font>

62
00:06:03,074 --> 00:06:05,404
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I, uh...</b></font>

63
00:06:05,404 --> 00:06:09,814
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I don't think I should see you anymore.</b></font>

64
00:06:25,524 --> 00:06:30,434
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>That's sudden. Can you tell me why?</b></font>

65
00:06:30,434 --> 00:06:34,564
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>There's someone I like now.</b></font>

66
00:06:41,514 --> 00:06:44,114
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I mean, I like you, too, Papa.</b></font>

67
00:06:44,114 --> 00:06:48,384
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>But this is a different kind of liking.</b></font>

68
00:06:50,454 --> 00:06:53,384
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Sorry I'm so selfish.</b></font>

69
00:07:13,074 --> 00:07:14,744
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>This is a joke.</i></b></font>

70
00:07:14,744 --> 00:07:18,184
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Why does my Evo IV have to stay cooped up</i></b></font>

71
00:07:18,184 --> 00:07:20,344
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>behind this ancient Eight-Six?</i></b></font>

72
00:07:20,344 --> 00:07:23,154
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>I can barely step on the gas.</i></b></font>

73
00:07:23,154 --> 00:07:25,524
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>I'm getting frustrated.</i></b></font>

74
00:07:25,524 --> 00:07:29,354
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>"Full Blast" is all that's in my Evo IV dictionary.</i></b></font>

75
00:07:29,354 --> 00:07:33,694
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Why use "Simulation 3" against this old junker?!</i></b></font>

76
00:07:33,694 --> 00:07:37,364
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>He's nowhere near that good, Kyoichi!</i></b></font>

77
00:07:41,004 --> 00:07:43,874
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Don't be impatient, Seiji.</i></b></font>

78
00:07:45,004 --> 00:07:48,274
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>What's this anger? I'm irritated!</i></b></font>

79
00:07:48,274 --> 00:07:50,904
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Why am I so irritated?!</i></b></font>

80
00:07:54,914 --> 00:07:56,914
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Hey, Keisuke?</b></font>

81
00:07:56,914 --> 00:08:00,124
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>What did Ryosuke say about this race?</b></font>

82
00:08:00,124 --> 00:08:02,294
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>He didn't say much.</b></font>

83
00:08:02,294 --> 00:08:06,864
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>He only told me to be at this
spot if I wanted to watch.</b></font>

84
00:08:06,864 --> 00:08:09,464
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It sounds like there's a reason behind that.</b></font>

85
00:08:09,464 --> 00:08:10,804
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Yeah.</b></font>

86
00:08:10,804 --> 00:08:14,634
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It's common sense that the
Eight-Six can't win this battle.</b></font>

87
00:08:14,634 --> 00:08:18,844
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>He's racing a Lan-Evo, after all.</b></font>

88
00:08:18,844 --> 00:08:21,844
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Don't act like you know everything, Kenta.</b></font>

89
00:08:21,844 --> 00:08:25,384
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Isn't it also common sense that your S14</b></font>

90
00:08:25,384 --> 00:08:28,514
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>shouldn't be slower than an Eight-Six?</b></font>

91
00:08:30,014 --> 00:08:32,654
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Don't torment him, Keisuke.</b></font>

92
00:08:32,654 --> 00:08:35,654
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>The race against the Eight-Six</b></font>

93
00:08:35,654 --> 00:08:37,664
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>turned out to be a great experience for Kenta.</b></font>

94
00:08:37,664 --> 00:08:40,494
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Yeah, what do I care?</b></font>

95
00:08:42,364 --> 00:08:45,264
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>"Emperor" or whatever they're called,</b></font>

96
00:08:45,264 --> 00:08:47,934
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>one thing will be certain after this battle</b></font>

97
00:08:47,934 --> 00:08:52,374
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>against Takumi Fujiwara on Akina's downhill.</b></font>

98
00:08:55,014 --> 00:08:58,384
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>This is the longest straightaway on this course.</i></b></font>

99
00:08:58,384 --> 00:09:01,744
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>I can easily get ahead of him if I want.</i></b></font>

100
00:09:03,214 --> 00:09:06,984
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>If you get impatient and jump ahead, it's over.</b></font>

101
00:09:08,054 --> 00:09:11,284
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Damn it! I've had enough of this!</b></font>

102
00:09:12,724 --> 00:09:16,634
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>That's how everyone lost,
including my brother.</b></font>

103
00:09:16,634 --> 00:09:18,634
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>If you jump ahead, you lose?</b></font>

104
00:09:18,634 --> 00:09:21,834
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Right. Can you understand
that paradox, Kenta?</b></font>

105
00:09:22,834 --> 00:09:25,174
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Here I go!</b></font>

106
00:09:29,374 --> 00:09:32,744
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>"Simulation 3" or not, Kyoichi...</i></b></font>

107
00:09:35,384 --> 00:09:38,184
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>...I just have to win this race, right?!</b></font>

108
00:09:41,994 --> 00:09:44,324
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>He's fast.</i></b></font>

109
00:09:44,324 --> 00:09:48,034
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Now you'll see how outclassed you are.</i></b></font>

110
00:09:48,034 --> 00:09:50,764
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>I'll just keep blasting away</i></b></font>

111
00:09:50,764 --> 00:09:53,264
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>until you disappear from my rearview mirror.</i></b></font>

112
00:09:53,264 --> 00:09:55,704
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>See ya, Eight-Six!</i></b></font>

113
00:09:54,934 --> 00:09:56,904
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="66"><b>{\an5}"Mt. Akina Forest Park Skate Center"</b></font>

114
00:10:15,424 --> 00:10:18,094
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Would you please reconsider?</b></font>

115
00:10:18,094 --> 00:10:23,264
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>You really make my life worth living.</b></font>

116
00:10:23,264 --> 00:10:27,534
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I really don't mind if you have a boyfriend,</b></font>

117
00:10:27,534 --> 00:10:30,434
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>as long as we stay the same.</b></font>

118
00:10:30,434 --> 00:10:34,074
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I know, I can give you more gifts.</b></font>

119
00:10:34,074 --> 00:10:36,474
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Papa, stop.</b></font>

120
00:10:36,474 --> 00:10:38,944
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It's not that.</b></font>

121
00:10:43,984 --> 00:10:47,924
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I've always liked you, Papa.</b></font>

122
00:10:47,924 --> 00:10:50,224
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Despite our age difference,</b></font>

123
00:10:50,224 --> 00:10:52,394
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I thought it was normal to have</b></font>

124
00:10:52,394 --> 00:10:56,264
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>a relationship with the person I liked, but...</b></font>

125
00:10:56,264 --> 00:10:58,264
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>...now that I think about it,</b></font>

126
00:10:58,264 --> 00:11:01,004
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>that's why you were giving me gifts.</b></font>

127
00:11:01,004 --> 00:11:03,834
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>This can't be normal.</b></font>

128
00:11:05,344 --> 00:11:08,714
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Do you really like this boy...</b></font>

129
00:11:08,714 --> 00:11:11,614
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>...that much?</b></font>

130
00:11:11,614 --> 00:11:15,514
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I probably do.</b></font>

131
00:11:15,514 --> 00:11:19,854
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Right now, that's all I can say.</b></font>

132
00:11:19,854 --> 00:11:23,354
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>What? Seiji got ahead of the Eight-Six?!</b></font>

133
00:11:23,354 --> 00:11:26,464
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>--He's pulling away!
--All right!</b></font>

134
00:11:26,464 --> 00:11:28,554
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I knew it.</b></font>

135
00:11:29,934 --> 00:11:33,104
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>That's the Seiji we know. He's gone now!</b></font>

136
00:11:33,104 --> 00:11:35,804
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>--That Eight-Six is nothing!
--Yeah!</b></font>

137
00:11:35,804 --> 00:11:38,874
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Despite his looks, Seiji is highly skilled.</b></font>

138
00:11:38,874 --> 00:11:41,364
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>He won't lose now.</b></font>

139
00:11:44,084 --> 00:11:45,914
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Idiot!</b></font>

140
00:11:49,614 --> 00:11:54,954
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Seiji has mastered driving his Lan-Evo fast.</i></b></font>

141
00:11:54,954 --> 00:11:58,124
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>He knows that a 4WD car has to enter a corner</i></b></font>

142
00:11:58,124 --> 00:12:01,024
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>at top speed to be able to drift through it.</i></b></font>

143
00:12:11,604 --> 00:12:15,514
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>During the drift, you can only control the car</i></b></font>

144
00:12:15,514 --> 00:12:19,544
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>by steering while flooring the gas pedal.</i></b></font>

145
00:12:19,544 --> 00:12:23,114
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>The car tends to fishtail if you try to control it</i></b></font>

146
00:12:23,114 --> 00:12:26,054
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>with the pedal like you would an FR.</i></b></font>

147
00:12:26,054 --> 00:12:30,794
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Full acceleration is the 4WD's way.</i></b></font>

148
00:12:30,794 --> 00:12:36,294
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>That's the hardest thing</i>
<i>about driving a 4WD car.</i></b></font>

149
00:12:36,294 --> 00:12:41,974
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>No mediocre racer can turn with full control.</i></b></font>

150
00:12:41,974 --> 00:12:45,144
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>But once you master the technique,</i></b></font>

151
00:12:45,144 --> 00:12:50,304
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>you can turn any corner</i>
<i>at remarkably high speed.</i></b></font>

152
00:12:56,084 --> 00:13:00,284
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>I guess I don't have to worry about Seiji, but...</i></b></font>

153
00:13:02,554 --> 00:13:05,924
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>...why am I feeling so anxious?</i></b></font>

154
00:13:13,834 --> 00:13:17,174
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Enter with speed and turn with full acceleration.</i></b></font>

155
00:13:17,174 --> 00:13:21,574
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>It's completely different from</i>
<i>the junker FR's slow "crab" turn.</i></b></font>

156
00:13:21,574 --> 00:13:24,214
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Watch me and learn.</i></b></font>

157
00:13:24,214 --> 00:13:28,284
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Of course, he has to be close by to see it.</i></b></font>

158
00:13:28,284 --> 00:13:30,454
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>I doubt he's anywhere near me.</i></b></font>

159
00:13:30,454 --> 00:13:32,084
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>He's so far...</i></b></font>

160
00:13:33,584 --> 00:13:35,354
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>What?!</i></b></font>

161
00:13:39,864 --> 00:13:42,864
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>He's right behind me instead of far back!</i></b></font>

162
00:13:42,864 --> 00:13:44,364
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>That's impossible!</i></b></font>

163
00:13:44,364 --> 00:13:47,134
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>He can keep up with my drift?</i></b></font>

164
00:13:47,134 --> 00:13:51,094
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>He's better than I thought. I see.</i></b></font>

165
00:14:23,074 --> 00:14:24,674
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>I get it now.</i></b></font>

166
00:14:24,674 --> 00:14:26,944
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>My irritation didn't come</i></b></font>

167
00:14:26,944 --> 00:14:30,774
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>from not being able to</i>
<i>speed up on the straightaways.</i></b></font>

168
00:14:30,774 --> 00:14:33,884
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>I guess I was aware of the actual reason</i></b></font>

169
00:14:33,884 --> 00:14:36,754
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>while I was following him.</i></b></font>

170
00:14:39,854 --> 00:14:46,124
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>I hate to admit it, but I... I...</i></b></font>

171
00:14:46,124 --> 00:14:48,524
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>I'm slower at corners!</i></b></font>

172
00:14:53,534 --> 00:14:57,264
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>So far, I've managed to keep up with him.</i></b></font>

173
00:15:03,544 --> 00:15:05,884
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>There's one more thing.</i></b></font>

174
00:15:05,884 --> 00:15:08,484
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>The straightaways are shorter around here,</i></b></font>

175
00:15:08,484 --> 00:15:11,684
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>and the difference in power</i>
<i>doesn't matter much.</i></b></font>

176
00:15:11,684 --> 00:15:13,384
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>But just wait.</i></b></font>

177
00:15:13,384 --> 00:15:15,724
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>In the upcoming high-speed section,</i></b></font>

178
00:15:15,724 --> 00:15:18,064
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>I'll erase you from my rearview mirror.</i></b></font>

179
00:15:18,064 --> 00:15:21,864
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>I bet my Lan-Evo racer's pride on it!</i></b></font>

180
00:15:34,074 --> 00:15:37,444
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>At the end of a long,</i>
<i>accelerating straightaway</i></b></font>

181
00:15:37,444 --> 00:15:39,284
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>waits a hairpin turn.</i></b></font>

182
00:15:39,284 --> 00:15:41,614
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>That's how it is.</i></b></font>

183
00:15:42,614 --> 00:15:44,454
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Here it comes.</i></b></font>

184
00:15:44,454 --> 00:15:47,254
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>I'll outrace you with my technique,</i></b></font>

185
00:15:47,254 --> 00:15:49,694
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>not my machine's capabilities.</i></b></font>

186
00:16:01,304 --> 00:16:04,844
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>He's fast. He certainly is!</b></font>

187
00:16:04,844 --> 00:16:07,674
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>That's a very fast car.</b></font>

188
00:16:19,384 --> 00:16:21,984
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>They'll be here shortly.</b></font>

189
00:16:26,164 --> 00:16:28,164
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Here they come!</b></font>

190
00:16:28,164 --> 00:16:30,734
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>The Lan-Evo is ahead. He's charging in!</b></font>

191
00:16:30,734 --> 00:16:33,994
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Akina's famous five hairpin turns.</b></font>

192
00:16:46,344 --> 00:16:48,084
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>What power!</b></font>

193
00:16:48,084 --> 00:16:51,214
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It's like a WRC car.</b></font>

194
00:16:52,624 --> 00:16:54,624
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>The Eight-Six is way behind.</b></font>

195
00:16:54,624 --> 00:16:57,124
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I've never seen him this far behind</b></font>

196
00:16:57,124 --> 00:16:59,624
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>at the five hairpins in past races.</b></font>

197
00:16:59,624 --> 00:17:02,894
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Maybe the Eight-Six can't pull it off this time.</b></font>

198
00:17:02,894 --> 00:17:05,404
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>That car is too inferior.</b></font>

199
00:17:05,404 --> 00:17:07,304
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>There!</b></font>

200
00:17:07,304 --> 00:17:09,864
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>It's time to use the ditch!</i></b></font>

201
00:17:23,484 --> 00:17:24,984
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>That was fast.</b></font>

202
00:17:24,984 --> 00:17:28,084
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>How did he turn so fast?</b></font>

203
00:17:29,654 --> 00:17:33,154
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>See that, Masashi? That's Bunta's son.</b></font>

204
00:17:34,494 --> 00:17:36,164
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>You're kidding me!</b></font>

205
00:17:36,164 --> 00:17:39,834
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It sure looked like Bunta was driving it.</b></font>

206
00:17:39,834 --> 00:17:43,834
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>The sound alone shows how great he is.</b></font>

207
00:17:43,834 --> 00:17:45,844
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>He was flooring the pedal for a long time.</b></font>

208
00:17:45,844 --> 00:17:50,274
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>No normal 18-year-old has skills like that.</b></font>

209
00:17:50,274 --> 00:17:52,444
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Like father, like son.</b></font>

210
00:17:52,444 --> 00:17:54,344
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>But...</b></font>

211
00:17:54,344 --> 00:17:58,714
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>...that kind of driving
sure is rough on the engine.</b></font>

212
00:18:11,064 --> 00:18:13,694
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>These are tough turns.</i></b></font>

213
00:18:19,174 --> 00:18:22,674
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>But I don't think I lost any time.</i></b></font>

214
00:18:22,674 --> 00:18:24,174
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>No matter the car...</i></b></font>

215
00:18:24,174 --> 00:18:27,704
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>...any driver would lose speed on these turns.</i></b></font>

216
00:18:31,324 --> 00:18:35,344
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>I should be safe with this much of a lead.</i></b></font>

217
00:18:39,224 --> 00:18:40,854
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>What?!</i></b></font>

218
00:18:47,764 --> 00:18:51,864
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>What happened? This can't be!</b></font>

219
00:19:02,114 --> 00:19:03,984
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>This is humiliating.</b></font>

220
00:19:03,984 --> 00:19:06,154
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I can't shake him off,</b></font>

221
00:19:06,154 --> 00:19:08,224
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>even with my technique and power!</b></font>

222
00:19:08,224 --> 00:19:10,054
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>What is this?!</b></font>

223
00:19:11,724 --> 00:19:13,394
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Punk...</b></font>

224
00:19:13,394 --> 00:19:15,524
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Don't insult me!</b></font>

225
00:19:24,874 --> 00:19:26,974
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It's almost time.</b></font>

226
00:19:26,974 --> 00:19:32,244
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I wonder who's ahead,
the Lan-Evo or the Eight-Six?</b></font>

227
00:19:33,914 --> 00:19:36,214
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Keisuke, you said earlier</b></font>

228
00:19:36,214 --> 00:19:39,714
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>that the Lan-Evo would lose if he was in front.</b></font>

229
00:19:41,324 --> 00:19:43,394
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I know from my own experience</b></font>

230
00:19:43,394 --> 00:19:46,564
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>that he won't let you run away with the lead.</b></font>

231
00:19:46,564 --> 00:19:49,724
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>He sticks right with you like super glue.</b></font>

232
00:19:51,734 --> 00:19:54,404
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>If you get irritated and rely on the car's power</b></font>

233
00:19:54,404 --> 00:19:57,104
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>to shake him off, the tires deflate.</b></font>

234
00:20:00,774 --> 00:20:03,574
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Damn, he's right on me.</i></b></font>

235
00:20:03,574 --> 00:20:07,584
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>The key is how you use the tires.</b></font>

236
00:20:07,584 --> 00:20:10,084
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Anyone who jumps ahead
without knowing that...</b></font>

237
00:20:10,084 --> 00:20:11,884
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>...will lose.</b></font>

238
00:20:16,794 --> 00:20:20,094
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>The front tires are losing pressure.</i></b></font>

239
00:20:20,094 --> 00:20:24,394
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>This is irritating. I just can't stay focused.</i></b></font>

240
00:20:24,394 --> 00:20:28,874
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Don't panic. No need to shake him off.</i></b></font>

241
00:20:28,874 --> 00:20:31,304
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>I'll win if I keep my lead.</i></b></font>

242
00:20:31,304 --> 00:20:34,914
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>I'm certainly in a more favorable position.</i></b></font>

243
00:20:34,914 --> 00:20:39,584
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>No matter how fast he can turn,</i>
<i>he can't pass me at a corner.</i></b></font>

244
00:20:39,584 --> 00:20:42,884
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>And I'm way faster on the straightaways!</i></b></font>

245
00:20:48,094 --> 00:20:49,794
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>I wasn't wrong.</i></b></font>

246
00:20:49,794 --> 00:20:53,464
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Taking the lead back there was the right move.</i></b></font>

247
00:20:53,464 --> 00:20:56,264
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>I'm the winner, Kyoichi!</i></b></font>

248
00:21:19,384 --> 00:21:24,294
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Whenever I turned around</i></b></font>

249
00:21:24,294 --> 00:21:29,564
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>There was always that</i>
<i>unchanging smile of yours</i></b></font>

250
00:21:29,564 --> 00:21:34,234
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>It was there on days when</i>
<i>I was too tired to go on</i></b></font>

251
00:21:34,234 --> 00:21:43,044
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>And even on days with a little happiness in them</i></b></font>

252
00:21:43,044 --> 00:21:51,624
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>My hands aren't enough</i></b></font>

253
00:21:51,624 --> 00:21:58,724
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>To hold on to all the love you gave me</i></b></font>

254
00:22:00,724 --> 00:22:07,864
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>The warm wind</i></b></font>

255
00:22:07,864 --> 00:22:15,544
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Comes back quietly and tenderly</i></b></font>

256
00:22:15,544 --> 00:22:23,554
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>And as I gaze at the sky alone</i></b></font>

257
00:22:23,554 --> 00:22:30,794
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>You smile down upon me</i></b></font>

258
00:22:30,794 --> 00:22:38,704
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>You are still waving to me from the radiant light</i></b></font>

259
00:22:38,704 --> 00:22:48,694
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Just like you did that day</i></b></font>

260
00:22:51,384 --> 00:22:57,084
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>You are my everlasting memory</i></b></font>

261
00:23:04,224 --> 00:23:08,764
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>The end is near. What did Takumi</i>
<i>decide during this tough race?</i></b></font>

262
00:23:08,764 --> 00:23:10,934
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Next on Initial D: Second Stage...</i></b></font>

263
00:23:10,934 --> 00:23:12,704
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>"Hollow Victory."</i></b></font>

264
00:23:12,704 --> 00:23:14,264
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Don't miss it!</i></b></font>

